  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/ee331782cbaaf5c1128eddfb78bf8c3e.avif?t=1772593946\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tails of Trainspot is a relaxing logic puzzle game set on the peaceful Packan Islands. Lay railway tracks to connect numbered stations, uncover the island’s secrets, and meet charming animal residents. With a gentle pace, cozy art style, and delightful mini-games, it's a thoughtful escape into a world of whimsy and wonder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/16a0ad35c5a15f506dc46d364c7c4b48.poster.avif?t=1772593946\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/16a0ad35c5a15f506dc46d364c7c4b48.webm?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/16a0ad35c5a15f506dc46d364c7c4b48.mp4?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/1550eebc37e7f24552c5c7285fa12678.avif?t=1772593946\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Logic Puzzle Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve grid-based puzzles where each station’s number tells you how many rails must connect to it. Plan your routes carefully—rails can’t cross or overlap, and every station must be part of a single connected network. Simple to learn, deeply satisfying to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/2e6d03c7279ff3a2b2975af6f07a21af.poster.avif?t=1772593946\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/2e6d03c7279ff3a2b2975af6f07a21af.webm?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/2e6d03c7279ff3a2b2975af6f07a21af.mp4?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A World Full of Stories</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore the islands, you'll meet curious animal residents and uncover hidden myths buried in ruins. The Packan Islands are more than just a puzzle board—they’re a living world filled with character and charm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/20ef21626de7f78759b986aad78295b5.poster.avif?t=1772593946\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/20ef21626de7f78759b986aad78295b5.webm?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/20ef21626de7f78759b986aad78295b5.mp4?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mini-Games for Variety</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a break from rail building with cozy side activities. Assemble bento boxes, run a drink bar, or roll sausage dice with the locals. These mini-games add warmth and variety to your island journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/ed47cca61d84b52c8de1863c7976d97a.poster.avif?t=1772593946\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/ed47cca61d84b52c8de1863c7976d97a.webm?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/ed47cca61d84b52c8de1863c7976d97a.mp4?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Relaxing Yet Rewarding</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With its soft, industrial-age aesthetic and calming soundscape, Tails of Trainspot is designed to soothe while still offering satisfying challenges. Perfect for puzzle lovers looking to unwind without sacrificing depth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Let the tracks guide you through tales, tea, and tranquility.</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/ee331782cbaaf5c1128eddfb78bf8c3e.avif?t=1772593946\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tails of Trainspot is a relaxing logic puzzle game set on the peaceful Packan Islands. Lay railway tracks to connect numbered stations, uncover the island’s secrets, and meet charming animal residents. With a gentle pace, cozy art style, and delightful mini-games, it's a thoughtful escape into a world of whimsy and wonder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/16a0ad35c5a15f506dc46d364c7c4b48.poster.avif?t=1772593946\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/16a0ad35c5a15f506dc46d364c7c4b48.webm?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/16a0ad35c5a15f506dc46d364c7c4b48.mp4?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/1550eebc37e7f24552c5c7285fa12678.avif?t=1772593946\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Logic Puzzle Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve grid-based puzzles where each station’s number tells you how many rails must connect to it. Plan your routes carefully—rails can’t cross or overlap, and every station must be part of a single connected network. Simple to learn, deeply satisfying to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/2e6d03c7279ff3a2b2975af6f07a21af.poster.avif?t=1772593946\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/2e6d03c7279ff3a2b2975af6f07a21af.webm?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/2e6d03c7279ff3a2b2975af6f07a21af.mp4?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A World Full of Stories</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore the islands, you'll meet curious animal residents and uncover hidden myths buried in ruins. The Packan Islands are more than just a puzzle board—they’re a living world filled with character and charm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/20ef21626de7f78759b986aad78295b5.poster.avif?t=1772593946\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/20ef21626de7f78759b986aad78295b5.webm?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/20ef21626de7f78759b986aad78295b5.mp4?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mini-Games for Variety</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a break from rail building with cozy side activities. Assemble bento boxes, run a drink bar, or roll sausage dice with the locals. These mini-games add warmth and variety to your island journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/ed47cca61d84b52c8de1863c7976d97a.poster.avif?t=1772593946\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/ed47cca61d84b52c8de1863c7976d97a.webm?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1302850/extras/ed47cca61d84b52c8de1863c7976d97a.mp4?t=1772593946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Relaxing Yet Rewarding</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With its soft, industrial-age aesthetic and calming soundscape, Tails of Trainspot is designed to soothe while still offering satisfying challenges. Perfect for puzzle lovers looking to unwind without sacrificing depth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Let the tracks guide you through tales, tea, and tranquility.</strong></p>",
